title: Episode 38 - Libby Trickett Interview (Brink Vault 2014)
itunes:title: Episode 38 - Libby Trickett Interview (Brink Vault 2014)
description: A 'vault' interview of epic proportion today as we go back to 2014 to speak with legendary Australian swimmer Libby Trickett! Talking up her then new role on Australian TV through to her career, things don't start the smoothest during the interview though as Ben makes one epic blunder. What is it? Well you'll have to listen to find out!
